11:52.612 --> 11:53.978
Try to drop it.

11:56.049 --> 11:57.482
Very good.

12:19.306 --> 12:22.474
Ok, ok, ok. Don't worry.

12:24.144 --> 12:25.510
Try again.

12:26.747 --> 12:27.979
