I'll be back later. Wait, wait.

12:53.273 --> 12:56.407
Alice sit down.

12:58.145 --> 13:00.211
She's not your mum.

13:06.486 --> 13:09.654
You know that I hate you,
don't you?

13:12.592 --> 13:13.792
