13:15.095 --> 13:16.461
Good.

13:49.796 --> 13:51.396
What is it?

13:55.836 --> 13:57.402
Don't know.

17:03.723 --> 17:05.423
Where is dad?

17:40.794 --> 17:42.693
Alice!

17:43.396 --> 17:45.163
Alice!

17:46.132 --> 17:47.799
Alice!

17:50.170 --> 17:52.136
Alice!

19:22.395 --> 19:23.895
What's your name?

19:28.101 --> 19:30.401
His name is Paul.

19:31.738 --> 19:33.938
I am Erika.

19:35.475 --> 19:37.141
He doesn't talk.

19:38.811 --> 19:40.244
Is he mute?

19:40.613 --> 19:43.047
Yes. Kind of.

19:45.084 --> 19:46.951
I'm Alice.

19:47.353 --> 19:49.620
He is my father, Adam.

19:50.256 --> 19:52.990
And she is my mother, Beatrice.

19:56.863 --> 19:58.229
Erika,

20:00.266 --> 20:01.799
who did this?

20:04.137 --> 20:07.939
If you don't tell us, we'll have
to call the police.

20:09.442 --> 20:10.775
David.

20:12.045 --> 20:14.278
He is my boyfriend.

20:16.349 --> 20:19.417
This morning he called me to go
make a picnic.

20:21.454 --> 20:24.021
I asked him if Paul could come
with us.

20:24.991 --> 20:26.824
"No".

20:28.027 --> 20:30.127
But Paul followed me,

20:30.830 --> 20:32.430
and he saw us.

20:41.507 --> 20:43.374
I asked him to stop,

20:43.943 --> 20:46.577
that Paul was there, but he
wouldn't.

20:48.715 --> 20:50.648
So I hit him.

20:51.751 --> 20:54.218
And he got very angry.

20:55.388 --> 20:58.289
I had never seen him like that
before.

21:00.760 --> 21:02.860
Where does David live?

21:06.232 --> 21:10.067
I don't know. He never took me
to his house.

21:14.207 --> 21:15.773
And where do you live?

21:17.343 --> 21:18.743
In town.

21:19.078 --> 21:20.778
With your parents?

21:23.283 --> 21:25.182
They're dead.

21:34.594 --> 21:36.427
I'm gonna prepare you a room.

21:37.163 --> 21:39.330
And tomorrow I'll take you home.

21:40.066 --> 21:47.405
And don't worry... the
house is shielded, the doors

21:47.407 --> 21:50.808
