be opened from the outside.

21:55.148 --> 21:56.814
Is that ok to you?

22:28.815 --> 22:31.048
Do you feel better now?

22:37.090 --> 22:39.557
Everything's going to be
alright.

22:40.693 --> 22:42.760
Don't think about David.

22:56.008 --> 22:58.075
What do you think about her?

23:01.714 --> 23:05.316
Do you like her?

23:50.563 --> 23:52.797
I just came to see if you were
alright.

23:53.132 --> 23:55.132
