26:25.184 --> 26:26.717
There's nothing there.

26:34.860 --> 26:38.729
There was something black behind
of those bushes in front of you.

26:41.601 --> 26:45.269
Wait, it's not there anymore.
It's... it's moved.

26:48.741 --> 26:53.811
What's that over there? That black
thing behind that bush over there.

26:58.217 --> 26:59.750
What happened?

27:01.554 --> 27:06.256
It's nothing. Don't worry, you
can go to bed.

27:07.393 --> 27:08.792
