32:29.315 --> 32:31.481
Where is your sister?

32:34.320 --> 32:36.286
Where is your sister?

33:17.329 --> 33:20.297
Alice! Alice come back!

33:21.266 --> 33:22.632
Alice!

33:24.703 --> 33:25.902
Alice.

33:28.240 --> 33:31.041
How do you do it in front of
her?

33:31.910 --> 33:33.176
