33:33.645 --> 33:37.147
Touch her face! In front of mum!

33:37.649 --> 33:39.416
Touch that bitch!

33:42.321 --> 33:44.287
She's not your mum.

33:45.391 --> 33:48.992
You son of a bitch, yes she is!

33:50.229 --> 33:51.995
No baby, she's not your mum.

33:51.997 --> 33:56.566
Yes she is! You transformed her!
She's like that because of you!

33:56.769 --> 33:59.036
You transformed me too!

33:59.505 --> 34:02.139
Look at what you've done!

34:03.542 --> 34:04.574
Look!

34:06.311 --> 34:07.611
I'm sorry.

34:08.647 --> 34:10.947
Alice, Alice I'm sorry.

34:13.485 --> 34:15.552
We're not the same anymore.

34:16.422 --> 34:17.487
That's not...

34:17.489 --> 34:19.489
We're not the same anymore.

34:20.458 --> 34:23.760
Yes, we're different!

34:24.730 --> 34:27.531
No baby, no. You're not.

34:27.733 --> 34:30.567
