killed her, I killed her... No, look!

34:49.288 --> 34:53.824
No! No! No! Baby, baby, listen.

34:53.826 --> 34:58.795
Listen to me, listen to me,
honey, honey, honey... No!

35:00.933 --> 35:02.365
Forgive me.

35:02.968 --> 35:05.268
I can't, I'm sorry.

35:07.039 --> 35:11.108
Forgive me, please.
I swear I tried but I can't.

35:14.813 --> 35:18.181
Tell her you're sorry. Tell mum
that you're sorry.

35:18.851 --> 35:20.750
Go tell her now.

35:22.721 --> 35:24.321
I can't do that.

35:26.425 --> 35:29.226
Tell her you're sorry!
I can't do that.

35:31.897 --> 35:33.897
I can't do that baby.

35:35.534 --> 35:41.071
You didn't love her you fucking
murderer!

35:41.440 --> 35:45.675
You didn't love her, you're a
fucking murderer! Don't say that.

35:46.411 --> 35:47.677
Don't say that.

35:50.349 --> 35:52.415
Tell mum that you're sorry!

35:52.684 --> 35:53.684
No.

35:53.986 --> 35:55.418
Tell her!

35:55.420 --> 36:01.992
No, I won't! I won't tell her I'm sorry!
I won't tell her anything!

38:59.771 --> 39:01.171
Are you sure?

39:02.107 --> 39:03.373
Yes.

39:03.975 --> 39:07.811
But Alice, maybe the girl in the
listening is not you.

39:08.213 --> 39:10.714
It's me.

39:10.715 --> 39:13.216
And how is it that she is able
to use the cube and you're not?

39:15.587 --> 39:17.687
'Cause it hasn't happened yet.

39:17.989 --> 39:21.358
I don't think I would trust her.
It could be a trap.

39:22.627 --> 39:26.563
She will explain everything to
me. She will explain who they

39:26.565 --> 39:31.968
are and how the cube works. She
will help me fix everything.

39:33.572 --> 39:34.572
Mum?

39:35.173 --> 39:36.940
Yes sweetheart, tell me.

39:37.409 --> 39:38.942
Do you love me?

39:39.511 --> 39:43.346
I love you so much. More than
anything in this world.

39:43.915 --> 39:45.348
So do I.

40:06.338 --> 40:07.337
Hello.

40:07.339 --> 40:08.571
Hi.

40:12.277 --> 40:14.277
I know this is very weird.

40:14.279 --> 40:16.897
You said it.

40:16.898 --> 40:19.516
You have to prepare. If you're
sitting down, get up.

40:20.819 --> 40:23.186
First and foremost, don't get
nervous.

40:23.455 --> 40:25.688
No one must know I'm talking to
you.

40:26.191 --> 40:30.326
Erika and Paul might hear us. They might
even be listening to us right now.

40:30.529 --> 40:33.229
You have to be careful. You
mustn't trust them.

40:33.231 --> 40:35.031
I need you to do something.

40:35.967 --> 40:38.034
What? It's something important.

40:38.503 --> 40:41.671
We'll do it step by step.
It'll be easier. No.

40:41.673 --> 40:46.676
First, tell me what the cube is. First of all,
you have to go see dad. He's in the piano room.

40:46.678 --> 40:48.945
No!

40:48.946 --> 40:51.213
Tell him that you've seen David.
Make sure he goes outside the house.

40:51.216 --> 40:53.516
And above all, don't let him
call the police,

40:53.518 --> 40:55.718
It always goes wrong when he
does it.

40:55.720 --> 40:56.853
What?

40:58.089 --> 41:00.290
Go now and leave mum in the
room.

41:00.725 --> 41:03.259
She must not go with you, it'll
be easier.

41:03.261 --> 41:07.630
Hurry up, we don't have much time.
If they notice it'll be too late.

41:30.088 --> 41:36.259
Are you with dad yet? I hope I'm not going
too fast. It's difficult to calculate.

41:48.273 --> 41:49.273
Dad?

41:53.645 --> 41:55.378
I'm sorry baby.

41:58.049 --> 42:00.049
I think I've seen someone
outside.

42:03.255 --> 42:04.521
Where are they?

42:05.023 --> 42:07.357
They're ok. They're in their
room.

42:12.130 --> 42:13.963
Ok, I'm gonna call the police.

42:13.965 --> 42:17.233
Wait, wait, wait please don't,
don't, don't call them.

42:17.235 --> 42:18.501
Why not?

42:25.010 --> 42:29.946
Well... Erika told me that she
wouldn't report him because...

42:30.282 --> 42:35.051
she doesn't want that... for Paul... I'm
sure that a scare will be enough...

42:39.391 --> 42:41.658
Ok. Listen.

42:41.893 --> 42:45.261
Just go to them. Don't tell them
anything.

42:45.997 --> 42:47.664
- Ok?
- Ok.

42:47.666 --> 42:49.666
I'll go have a look around.

42:52.504 --> 42:53.504
Dad?

42:53.939 --> 42:54.938
Yeah?

42:54.940 --> 42:59.008
Now go to
the kitchen and look for Paul.

43:01.079 --> 43:02.545
Be careful.

43:05.417 --> 43:06.449
Yeah.

43:20.065 --> 43:24.233
When you find him be aware. He mustn't
know that you're listening to me.

43:43.054 --> 43:44.220
Paul?

44:03.074 --> 44:04.074
Hi.

44:09.948 --> 44:11.581
Are you hungry?

44:29.734 --> 44:31.734
I can make a sandwich for the
two of us.

44:31.736 --> 44:33.536
Alice...

44:33.538 --> 44:37.173
I suppose you're already with him.
Erika will be here at any time.

44:37.509 --> 44:39.475
We have to do it now.

44:39.911 --> 44:41.177
Sit down.

44:54.092 --> 44:55.992
You have to grab a knife...

44:57.195 --> 44:58.528
and kill him.

45:01.366 --> 45:03.766
I know you're scared.
I'm scared too.

45:04.269 --> 45:06.102
And I know it's difficult.

45:06.671 --> 45:09.772
But you have to trust me.
Kill him.

45:12.477 --> 45:15.945
And when Erika arrives, kill
this bitch too.

45:24.155 --> 45:27.757
Do it quickly. We've done this
before.

45:28.560 --> 45:33.062
I can't remember how many times. And
it always ends up the same way.

45:33.765 --> 45:36.666
The only thing we haven't tried
is killing them.

45:49.647 --> 45:50.780
No!

45:53.251 --> 45:54.550
I can do it.

45:56.888 --> 46:01.524
Alice, I'm very tired. I don't know
if I will be able to carry on.

46:01.960 --> 46:05.228
If you don't do it something
terrible will happen.

46:05.663 --> 46:09.265
And it's better for you not to
know it. Do it now.

46:36.828 --> 46:40.163
I know that you like him but
don't trust him. Please!

46:40.899 --> 46:42.498
Kill him please.

46:46.271 --> 46:47.503
Kill him.

46:48.273 --> 46:49.505
Please.

46:51.509 --> 46:52.875
Kill him!

47:03.087 --> 47:05.855
I have to go. Good luck.

47:22.774 --> 47:24.874
What are you listening to?

47:26.878 --> 47:27.878
Nothing.

47:31.749 --> 47:33.316
Let me listen to it.

47:34.485 --> 47:37.620
I'm making a sandwich. Do you
want one?

47:40.959 --> 47:42.491
No, thank you.

47:47.031 --> 47:48.898
Have you seen your father?

47:49.667 --> 47:50.933
He's gone.

47:51.870 --> 47:52.870
Where?

47:54.772 --> 47:56.205
I don't know.

49:27.999 --> 49:32.301
You know what you have to do.

50:42.440 --> 50:43.440
Dog?

50:45.309 --> 50:47.276
Well... wait here.

55:50.915 --> 55:52.314
Mum?

55:55.720 --> 55:57.252
Mum?

56:29.587 --> 56:30.753
Mum?

56:39.163 --> 56:40.329
Mum?

57:21.372 --> 57:22.671
Mum.

57:28.446 --> 57:29.812
Mum?

57:35.853 --> 57:37.252
Mum?

