01:10:59.155 --> 01:11:00.922
Ok. I'm going out
look around there.

01:11:02.492 --> 01:11:03.492
Dad?

01:11:04.261 --> 01:11:05.261
Yeah.

01:11:09.032 --> 01:11:10.398
Be careful.

01:11:12.369 --> 01:11:13.369
Yeah.

01:11:13.803 --> 01:11:14.803
Ok.

